    • Method Detail

      • coordinates

        long[] coordinates()
        Coordinates of the place -- must be on its planet surface. Completely derived from the location of its planets code, the radius of the planet, and the direction from core.
        Returns:
        Coordinates of the place
        See Also:
        getDirectionFromCore()

      • getDirectionFromCore

        double[] getDirectionFromCore()
        Returns the direction from the core of the planet to the location of this place on its surface. Distance from core is always the radius of the planet.
        Returns:
        direction to this place from planets core.

      • setDirectionFromCore

        void setDirectionFromCore(double[] dir)
        Sets the direction from the core of the planet to the location of this place on its surface. Distance from core is always the radius of the planet.
        Parameters:
        dir - direction to this place from planets core.
